feat(portal): full spec dialog when clicking a catalog item

Clicking the photo (or title) of any card on the store-portal catalog
now opens a comprehensive details dialog so the store can see every
spec the supplier has on file before committing to a memo request.

- Image gallery (cover + additional pictures), thumbnail strip,
  optional 360-deg video link and certificate link for stones.
- Spec table covering shape, carat, color, clarity, cut/polish/symmetry,
  table/depth, ratio, measurements, lab, origin, treatment, fluorescence,
  fancy color attributes, pair SKU and certificate number for stones.
- For jewelry: metal mix, stones list (with thumbnail snapshots),
  description and full attribute grid.
- Pricing intentionally absent. Footer line reminds the store that
  pricing is set when the supplier issues the memo.
- Add to request / In your request CTA mirrored in the dialog footer.
